    {
      "num": "04 · the takeaway",
      "heading": "Limits protect the promise",
      "blocks": [
        {
          "type": "prose",
          "html": "<p class=\"body\">Rate limiting is reliability with manners: it preserves the service by making overload explicit.</p>"
        },
